# Jin Hong M&E V2 - Homepage (index.html) Redesign Plan

## Goal Description
The objective is to overhaul [index.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/index.html) to fully align with the newly established "Jin Hong M&E V2" premium design standard (MaxCoach patterns, Bootstrap 5, FontAwesome 6). The current [index.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/index.html) has a solid layout but lacks the depth of content and the structural consistency (Header/Footer, icons) applied to the interior pages during the recent V2 overhaul.

## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Global Structure Alignment
- **Header & Footer**: Replace the existing custom header and footer in [index.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/index.html) with the exact Bootstrap 5 compliant header and the dark-premium footer used in [about.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/about.html), [services.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html/services.html), etc.
- **Dependencies**: Inject Bootstrap 5 CSS/JS and FontAwesome 6 CSS into the `<head>` to support the new components.
- **Floating CTA**: Add the global floating WhatsApp button (`.float-wa`) to the bottom right.

### Component 2: Hero Slider & Intro Section
- **Hero Slider**: Keep the immersive Swiper slider, but ensure fonts and spacing align with the global CSS variables.
- **About/Intro Asymmetrical Grid**: Update the text to include deeper company philosophies derived from the JIN_HONG_read.pdf (already extracted into [about.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/about.html)).

### Component 3: The Bento Box (Why Choose Us)
- **Icons Update**: Replace the raw SVG paths with high-quality FontAwesome solid icons.
- **Content Expansion**: Enhance the text to emphasize the CIDB G7, ST Class A, and SPAN C1 certifications, as well as the 800+ local workforce advantage.

### Component 4: Deep Content Integration (Services & Projects)
- **Services Expansion**: Replace the 3 "Hover Cards" with the 6 premium MaxCoach service cards (with gradient hover lines) established in [services.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html/services.html) to provide a full overview of capabilities.
- **Projects Showcase [NEW SECTION]**: Introduce a "Featured Projects" section pulling the top 3 cards from [projects.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/projects.html) (e.g., GDS Data Center, EVE Factory, AT&S Factory) to immediately build trust on the homepage.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
The user can open [index.html](file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/maxcoach/index.html) in their browser to verify:
1. The header and footer perfectly visually match the interior pages.
2. The slider works smoothly.
3. The new Services Grid (6 items) and Projects Gallery (3 items) display with premium hover effects.
4. The WhatsApp button floats correctly and links to the correct number.
